siqgurU dI ikrpw nwl auh sMswr ivc vrqdw hoieAw hI mwieAw vloN audws rihMdw hY, qW aus dw mn Awpxy Awp ivc pqIj jWdw hY (bwhr BtkxoN ht jWdw hY)[
hy nwnk! ijn@W dw mn pqIijAw nhIN, auhnW nUM igAwn dIAW g`lW krn dw koeI lwB nhIN huMdw ]1]
